{"text_id":148873,"tokens":["Psycho","active"," substances"," can"," speed"," up"," the"," likelihood"," of"," developing"," a"," mental"," disorder"," in"," someone"," who"," is"," predis","posed"," to"," it"," through"," several"," mechanisms","."," ","1","."," Neuro","chemical"," Changes",":"," Psycho","active"," substances"," can"," alter"," the"," balance"," of"," neuro","transmitters"," in"," the"," brain",","," which"," are"," chemicals"," that"," transmit"," signals"," between"," nerve"," cells","."," These"," changes"," can"," trigger"," the"," onset"," of"," mental"," disorders"," in"," individuals"," who"," are"," genetically"," predis","posed"," to"," them","."," For"," example",","," substances"," like"," cocaine"," and"," amp","heta","mines"," increase"," the"," levels"," of"," dopamine",","," a"," neuro","transmitter"," associated"," with"," pleasure"," and"," reward","."," This"," can"," lead"," to"," the"," development"," of"," disorders"," like"," schizophrenia"," or"," bipolar"," disorder"," in"," susceptible"," individuals","."," ","2","."," Stress"," and"," Trauma",":"," The"," use"," of"," psycho","active"," substances"," can"," lead"," to"," stressful"," life"," events"," and"," trauma",","," such"," as"," relationship"," problems",","," job"," loss",","," or"," legal"," issues","."," These"," stressors"," can"," trigger"," the"," onset"," of"," mental"," disorders"," in"," individuals"," who"," are"," predis","posed"," to"," them","."," ","3","."," Brain"," Damage",":"," Some"," psycho","active"," substances"," can"," cause"," direct"," damage"," to"," the"," brain",","," which"," can"," lead"," to"," the"," development"," of"," mental"," disorders","."," For"," example",","," chronic"," alcohol"," use"," can"," lead"," to"," brain"," damage"," that"," results"," in"," cognitive"," deficits"," and"," mood"," disorders","."," ","4","."," Dual"," Diagnosis",":"," Often",","," individuals"," who"," are"," predis","posed"," to"," mental"," disorders"," may"," use"," psycho","active"," substances"," as"," a"," form"," of"," self","-","medication",","," leading"," to"," a"," cycle"," of"," addiction"," and"," worsening"," mental"," health"," symptoms","."," This"," is"," known"," as"," dual"," diagnosis"," or"," co","-","occurring"," disorders","."," ","5","."," Ep","ig","enetic"," Changes",":"," Recent"," research"," suggests"," that"," psycho","active"," substances"," can"," cause"," changes"," in"," gene"," expression"," that"," can"," increase"," the"," risk"," of"," mental"," disorders","."," These"," changes",","," known"," as"," epigenetic"," changes",","," can"," potentially"," be"," passed"," on"," to"," future"," generations","."," It","'","s"," important"," to"," note"," that"," not"," everyone"," who"," uses"," psycho","active"," substances"," will"," develop"," a"," mental"," disorder",","," and"," not"," everyone"," with"," a"," predisposition"," to"," mental"," disorders"," will"," have"," their"," condition"," triggered"," by"," substance"," use","."," However",","," the"," risk"," is"," significantly"," higher"," in"," these"," individuals",","," making"," substance"," use"," a"," major"," public"," health"," concern","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"gpt4","label":1}